Package: NetworkToolbox
Title: Network Filtering Methods and Measures
Version: 0.0.1.1
Author: Alexander Christensen
Maintainer: Alexander Christensen <alexpaulchristensen@gmail.com>
Description: Implements Information Filtering Networks (IFN; Barfuss, Massara, Di Matteo, & Aste (2016)), ECO (ECO; Fallani, Latora, & Chavez (2017) <doi:10.1371/journal.pcbi.1005305>), and regression-based filtering network approaches (including the dependency network approach; Kenett, Tumminello, Madi, Gur-Gershogoren, Mantegna, & Ben-Jacob (2010) <https://doi.org/10.1371/journal.pone.0015032>). Also implements several network measures like local network characteristics (e.g., centralities), global network characteristics (e.g., clustering coefficient), and edge replication (Rubinov and Sporns (2010) <doi:10.1016/j.neuroimage.2009.10.003>). Finally, there are a few bootstrapping techniques that are aimed at increasing the reliability and reproducibility of network analysis (Tumminello, Coronnello, & Lillo  <https://doi.org/10.1142/S0218127407018415>).
Depends: R (>= 3.3.0)
License: GPL (>= 3.0)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Imports:
    Matrix,
    devtools,
    psych,
    qgraph,
    corrplot,
